- Democratic Republic of the Congo: 0 case in 2018 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2017), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 25-Nov-17
- Pakistan: 0 case in 2018 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2017), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 17-Dec-16
- Nigeria: 0 case in 2018 (compared with 0 for the same period in 2017), onset of paralysis of most recent case: 28-Oct-16
